	<h1 class="title">《查理周刊》遇袭，苹果等大公司集体站台声援</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/2007/small/2007.jpg?1408114682" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">许冰清</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-12 16:49:05 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5149/medium/5149.jpg?1436679958" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


